accessed by the current IP [24]) to capture spatial locality,
enabling comprehensive pattern recognition. ITSM distributes
thepredictionprocessacrossthesefivedistinctMTs( C ),each
predicting the most likely next delta or stride for a given IP to
generate prediction addresses within the Zion prefetcher (D).

